OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Marion
OL,4,CLoveland
OL,6,FMarion Loveland, Age 102, Women's
OL,7,FRoyal Naval Service
OL,9,FInterviewed 3 April 2024
OL,11,FA Wren third officer at HMS
OL,12,FCollingwood in Hampshire at the time
OL,13,Fof the invasion, Mrs Loveland's fiance
OL,14,Fwas killed on D-Day and she read the
OL,15,Fnews of his death several days later
OL,16,Fwhile she was at work.
OL,18,FAlec Aldis was a Royal Marine Commando
OL,19,Fand among the first troops to storm
OL,20,FSword Beach in a motor torpedo boat.
