OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Marion
OL,4,CLoveland
OL,6,FHis body was never found.
OL,8,FMrs Loveland said: "He was a permanent
OL,9,FRoyal Marine officer, not just wartime.
OL,11,F"No known grave but the sea, and I
OL,12,Ftried to find out and talk to people
OL,13,Fthat were with him and there is very
OL,14,Flittle.
OL,16,F"They did tell me there was an awful
OL,17,Flot of smoke and you couldn't see from
OL,18,Fone to another on the beach."
