OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Marion
OL,4,CLoveland
OL,6,FThe two had been going out for some
OL,7,Ftime but Mrs Loveland's father was a
OL,8,Fsenior Naval officer.
OL,10,FTherefore Alec, who had received the
OL,11,FMilitary Medal while serving in Crete,
OL,12,Fhad wanted to wait before proposing.
OL,14,F"He had said 'Get leave at
OL,15,FChristmas,'" Mrs Loveland said. 'I'll
OL,16,Ftake you to meet my parents, and we'll
OL,17,Fmake it official'.
