OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Marion
OL,4,CLoveland
OL,6,F"We kept it secret because of my
OL,7,Ffather's rank. He wouldn't go and ask
OL,8,Fmy father to marry me until he felt
OL,9,Fsecure and had a good rank.
OL,11,F"When I look back, I think what a
OL,12,Flovely man he was.
OL,14,F"I didn't know until one or two days
OL,15,Fafter. Really it was such a shock when
OL,16,FI found out about Alec.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/7
